---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Abrir Ticket — CyberAct Tecnologia">

  <section class="min-h-[80vh] flex items-center section-padding">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 justify-center mb-8 animate-fade-up">
          <div class="h-px w-12 bg-cyber-red"></div>
          <span class="text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyber-red">Suporte</span>
          <div class="h-px w-12 bg-cyber-red"></div>
        </div>

        <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-cyber-white mb-6 animate-fade-up animate-delay-100">
          Área do <span class="text-cyber-red">Cliente</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-cyber-text leading-relaxed mb-4 animate-fade-up animate-delay-200">
          Abra um ticket de suporte, acompanhe seus atendimentos, consulte o histórico das últimas solicitações e receba um posicionamento do seu chamado.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm text-cyber-text/70 leading-relaxed mb-8 md:mb-12 animate-fade-up animate-delay-200">
          Você será redirecionado para a plataforma Zoho. Faça o cadastro e login — nosso time atenderá suas solicitações.
        </p>

        <div class="animate-fade-up animate-delay-300">
          <a href="#" target="_blank" class="btn-primary text-sm sm:text-base py-3 px-6 sm:py-4 sm:px-10">
            Abrir Ticket de Suporte
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 md:mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-6">
          <div class="card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center border border-cyber-border mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-cyber-red">
                <path d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-cyber-white mb-2">Abrir chamado</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-cyber-text">Descreva o problema e receba atendimento.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center border border-cyber-border mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-cyber-red">
                <path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-cyber-white mb-2">Acompanhar</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-cyber-text">Veja o status e posicionamento em tempo real.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 flex items-center justify-center border border-cyber-border mx-auto mb-4">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="text-cyber-red">
                <path d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-sm font-medium text-cyber-white mb-2">Histórico</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-cyber-text">Consulte todas as suas solicitações anteriores.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
